name: Penfield Gibson Navy , Army
description:
The Gibson is a zip through hooded jacket with classic Penfield features, making it the ideal lightweight option for when the wind blows, the rain falls or the sun shines. 

Constructed from our classic Penfield Hudson Wax Cloth, this densely woven fabric is windproof and extremely durable and thanks to its impregnation of enviromentally friendly wax the surface is also water resistant. The adjustable cuffs and hem cinch mean you can adapt the fit and feel of the Gibson, whilst the cork cord locks and contrasting white buttons finish off a practical yet stylish jacket. The Gibson has been updated for Spring/Summer 2013 with new colors such as ecru, royal blue and forest green.

name: Penfield Vassan Olive
description:
The Vassan parka is a lightweight, versatile great all-rounder and the perfect piece to take you from spring right through to those cool summer evenings. 

Constructed from the classic Penfield Hudson Wax Cloth, this densely woven fabric is windproof and extremely durable and thanks to its impregnation of environmentally friendly wax the surface is also water resistant. The adjustable hood cords, waist and hem cinches means you can adapt the fit and feel of the Vassan and four front pockets and the addition of a small sleeve pocket offer functionality. All the buttons are dyed to match the fabric, giving the Vassan a smarter feel. 

A classic shape with a hard-wearing yet lightweight, breathable construction means the Vassan performs in the wind and rain, yet feels comfortable even on a warm Summer’s day.

name: Penfield Greylock Navy
description:
New for Spring/Summer 2013 the Greylock is a lightweight jacket expedition parka that is ideal for early spring. 

Constructed from our classic Penfield Hudson Wax Cloth, this densely woven fabric is windproof and extremely durable, and thanks to its impregnation of environmentally friendly wax the surface is also water resistant. The lightweight nature of the fabric and underarm venting mean it can be worn through spring and summer and the chambray lining smartens up the jacket whilst still keeping you protected. The peaked hood and neck guard will also help keep the unpredictable spring weather at bay. 

Smart details like the chambray lining and wooden cinch cord locks mean the Greylock can be dressed up or down, making it a truly versatile piece for Spring/Summer 2013

name: Penfield Pearson Navy
